  <brief_title>Covid-19 Pandemic and Use of Video Laryngoscopy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Airway Management During the Covid-19 Pandemic: A Comparison of Direct Laryngoscopy Versus Video Laryngoscopy</official_title>
  <sponsors>
